[Malaria is endemic in Nigeria, and it is not possible from the report to know whether the cited figures is an increase or decrease compared to previous years. If it is an increase it would be interesting to have information on the use of impregnated bed nets and the availability of appropriate drugs for treatment like artemisinin combinations.

